longDescription:
Immerse yourself in an oasis of serenity and freshness with our collection of nature assets. This extensive package offers a wide variety of icons that capture the beauty and vitality of the natural world.


🌷 Flowers:

From bright daisies to lush roses and delicate wildflowers, each floral icon is meticulously designed to add a touch of colour and elegance to your project.


🌿 Grass and Greenery:

Bring your surroundings to life with a selection of grass and vegetation icons. From rolling meadows to dense forests, these assets add depth and realism to your scene.


🌳 Trees:

Elevate your project with the imposing presence of majestic trees. From sturdy oaks to slender spruces and lush willows, these icons provide a stunning, natural backdrop.


🥀 Natural Details:

In addition to flowers, grass and trees, this package includes a variety of natural details such as rocks, streams, mushrooms and more. These little touches add authenticity and realism to your virtual environment.
